    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. It is honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I have babied this car since day one, and it is still in pristine condition\u2014spotless inside and out. If you are looking for that 'new car' feel without the 'new car' price tag, this is definitely the one for you. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next adventure. Come by and take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
