    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Step into what can only be described as a time capsule. This vehicle is in absolute pristine condition, looking and smelling exactly as it did the day it rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish thanks to a professional-grade ceramic coating, with zero rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. Inside, the premium leather remains supple and uncreased, free from any scents or signs of wear. Every button, dial, and electronic feature functions flawlessly. Mechanically, this car has been pampered with an open-checkbook maintenance philosophy; it comes with a complete folder of service records and has always been garaged under a breathable cover. With exceptionally low mileage and a spotless history, this is a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast who settles for nothing less than perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
