      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 6
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in impeccable showroom condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a history of fastidious care and climate-controlled storage. Mechanically superior and aesthetically indistinguishable from new, this specimen is a definitive acquisition for the most discerning enthusiast who demands uncompromising quality.",
