    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape you\u2019d think it just rolled off the showroom floor yesterday! I've babied this car from day one, keeping it spotless and always parked under cover. It drives like a dream and still has that fresh feel inside. If you're looking for something that looks and feels brand new without the brand new price tag, this is the one for you. I'm sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it!",
      "price": 44900.0,
