    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S, a definitive 996.2 widebody featuring the robust 3.6L flat-six with VarioCam Plus. This naturally aspirated powerhouse is paired with a slick-shifting 6-speed Getrag manual transmission and a viscous-coupling AWD system. Mechanically superlative, this example features a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a clean DME report showing no Stage 2 overrevs. The chassis utilizes Turbo-spec suspension geometry and 4-piston monoblock calipers over ventilated, cross-drilled rotors for peak deceleration. Every seal is dry, the throttle mapping is razor-sharp, and the factory finish is preserved with exacting detail. A true turn-key enthusiast specimen with comprehensive service provenance.",
